            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Chronicles%2016%3A37-18%3A17%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_16_37%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2237%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EWorship%20at%20Jerusalem%20and%20Gibeon%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E37%3C%2Fspan%3EDavid%20arranged%20for%20Asaph%20and%20his%20fellow%20Levites%20to%20serve%20regularly%20before%20the%20Ark%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Covenant%2C%20doing%20whatever%20needed%20to%20be%20done%20each%20day.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_16_38%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2238%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E38%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20group%20included%20Obed-edom%20(son%20of%20Jeduthun)%2C%20Hosah%2C%20and%20sixty-eight%20other%20Levites%20as%20gatekeepers.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_16_39%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2239%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E39%3C%2Fspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20David%20stationed%20Zadok%20the%20priest%20and%20his%20fellow%20priests%20at%20the%20Tabernacle%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20at%20the%20place%20of%20worship%20in%20Gibeon%2C%20where%20they%20continued%20to%20minister%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_16_40%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2240%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E40%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20sacrificed%20the%20regular%20burnt%20offerings%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20each%20morning%20and%20evening%20on%20the%20altar%20set%20aside%20for%20that%20purpose%2C%20obeying%20everything%20written%20in%20the%20Law%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20as%20he%20had%20commanded%20Israel.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_16_41%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2241%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E41%3C%2Fspan%3EDavid%20also%20appointed%20Heman%2C%20Jeduthun%2C%20and%20the%20others%20chosen%20by%20name%20to%20give%20thanks%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20for%20%26%23x201C%3Bhis%20faithful%20love%20endures%20forever.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_16_42%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2242%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E42%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20used%20their%20trumpets%2C%20cymbals%2C%20and%20other%20instruments%20to%20accompany%20their%20songs%20of%20praise%20to%20God.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E16%3A42%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Eto%20accompany%20the%20sacred%20music%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Eto%20accompany%20singing%20to%20God.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20And%20the%20sons%20of%20Jeduthun%20were%20appointed%20as%20gatekeepers.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_16_43%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%2243%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E43%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20all%20the%20people%20returned%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20and%20David%20turned%20and%20went%20home%20to%20bless%20his%20own%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_17_1%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E1%20Chronicles%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22subhead-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Covenant%20Promise%20to%20David%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20David%20was%20settled%20in%20his%20palace%2C%20he%20summoned%20Nathan%20the%20prophet.%20%26%23x201C%3BLook%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20David%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20am%20living%20in%20a%20beautiful%20cedar%20palace%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E17%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ea%20house%20of%20cedar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20but%20the%20Ark%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Covenant%20is%20out%20there%20under%20a%20tent!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_17_2%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ENathan%20replied%20to%20David%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BDo%20whatever%20you%20have%20in%20mind%2C%20for%20God%20is%20with%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_17_3%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20that%20same%20night%20God%20said%20to%20Nathan%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_17_4%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-fl-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGo%20and%20tell%20my%20servant%20David%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20declared%3A%20You%20are%20not%20the%20one%20to%20build%20a%20house%20for%20me%20to%20live%20in.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_17_5%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20have%20never%20lived%20in%20a%20house%2C%20from%20the%20day%20I%20brought%20the%20Israelites%20out%20of%20Egypt%20until%20this%20very%20day.%20My%20home%20has%20always%20been%20a%20tent%2C%20moving%20from%20one%20place%20to%20another%20in%20a%20Tabernacle.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_17_6%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EYet%20no%20matter%20where%20I%20have%20gone%20with%20the%20Israelites%2C%20I%20have%20never%20once%20complained%20to%20Israel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20leaders%2C%20the%20shepherds%20of%20my%20people.%20I%20have%20never%20asked%20them%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWhy%20haven%26%23x2019%3Bt%20you%20built%20me%20a%20beautiful%20cedar%20house%3F%26%23x201D%3B%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_17_7%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BNow%20go%20and%20say%20to%20my%20servant%20David%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%20has%20declared%3A%20I%20took%20you%20from%20tending%20sheep%20in%20the%20pasture%20and%20selected%20you%20to%20be%20the%20leader%20of%20my%20people%20Israel.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_17_8%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20have%20been%20with%20you%20wherever%20you%20have%20gone%2C%20and%20I%20have%20destroyed%20all%20your%20enemies%20before%20your%20eyes.%20Now%20I%20will%20make%20your%20name%20as%20famous%20as%20anyone%20who%20has%20ever%20lived%20on%20the%20earth!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_17_9%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20I%20will%20provide%20a%20homeland%20for%20my%20people%20Israel%2C%20planting%20them%20in%20a%20secure%20place%20where%20they%20will%20never%20be%20disturbed.%20Evil%20nations%20won%26%23x2019%3Bt%20oppress%20them%20as%20they%26%23x2019%3Bve%20done%20in%20the%20past%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_17_10%22%20bk%3D