ort%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-fl-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Nathan%20went%20back%20to%20David%20and%20told%20him%20everything%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20said%20in%20this%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_17_16%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EDavid%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Prayer%20of%20Thanks%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20King%20David%20went%20in%20and%20sat%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20prayed%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-fl-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BWho%20am%20I%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20God%2C%20and%20what%20is%20my%20family%2C%20that%20you%20have%20brought%20me%20this%20far%3F%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_17_17%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20now%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3BGod%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20everything%20else%2C%20you%20speak%20of%20giving%20your%20servant%20a%20lasting%20dynasty!%20You%20speak%20as%20though%20I%20were%20someone%20very%20great%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E17%3A17%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20meaning%20of%20the%20Hebrew%20is%20uncertain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20O%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20God!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_17_18%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20more%20can%20I%20say%20to%20you%20about%20the%20way%20you%20have%20honored%20me%3F%20You%20know%20what%20your%20servant%20is%20really%20like.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_17_19%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%